Process called "calculate_bollinger_bands" that takes prices as NDArray.NDArray and period as Integer and std_multiplier as Float returns BollingerBandsData:
    Let ma_data be calculate_moving_average with prices as prices and period as period and ma_type as "simple"
    Let upper_band be NDArray.copy_array with arr as ma_data
    Let lower_band be NDArray.copy_array with arr as ma_data Note: Simplified implementation - would need rolling standard deviation
    For i from 0 to ma_data.size - 1:
    Let ma_val be Float.from with value as ma_data.data at index i
    Let band_width be ma_val multiplied by 0.1 multiplied by std_multiplier
    Set upper_band.data at index i to ma_val band_width
    Set lower_band.data at index i to ma_val - band_width Return BollingerBandsData with:
    upper_band as upper_band
    middle_band as ma_data
    lower_band as lower_band

